room_title: Escape room "Darkness Falls" by Locked In Escapes in Colorado Springs
room_address: 2760 N Academy Blvd Suite 301 Colorado Springs, CO 80917
room_description: Stories have circulated regarding the disappearance of people in the Rocky Mountain National Forest.  You and your fellow Investigative reporters have followed a lead and may have found an abandoned cabin at the center of these disappearances. Can you discover the secrets within and escape before darkness falls?
